title: Goldspot - Tally Of The Yes Men
description:
LA- based Goldpsot, the brainchild of songwriter Siddhartha Khosla features completely different artwork than the U.S. pressing released in 2006. Having already supported Travis in the U.S., the band are touring the UK, culminating in a slot at Glastonbury in the Q Tent! Stand out tracks on the album include the Difford & Tilbrook-like 'Time Bomb' plus 'Rewind' and 'Friday', which is the first single, blending a subtle range of sounds from Bollywood to REM to The Smiths. Mercury.
